{"tid":2264434,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【ViuTV】羅嘉駿導演 奇幻愛情穿越劇《二月廿九》×《940920》討論 (99)","createTime":"2020-10-30T15:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T15:36:52.000Z","uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f517476c57c44d3d6db8ed8858125d28bee6bb5","tid":2264434,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"《二月廿九》四年一遇 聚散有時<br />\n三位主角 徐天佑、吳海昕、劉俊謙<br />\n<br />\n《二月廿九》攞獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />世界第一！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5GMbrg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5GMbrg.png&h=abe9108e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《940920》羅嘉駿 導演作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nKBd_MboacE&amp;ab_channel=SteveLaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnKBd_MboacE%26ab_channel%3DSteveLaw&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=3e1c2cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nKBd_MboacE&amp;ab_channel=SteveLaw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5j36VTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5j36VTa.jpg&h=6afa0182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9wHudc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9wHudc.jpg&h=79497ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6KJX6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6KJX6z.jpg&h=a7239546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你哋仲記唔記得sofiee有咩金句呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKdOpMG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKdOpMG.png&h=94af6b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avEQovV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avEQovV</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS: 寶庫區已經更新咗，歡迎閲覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在此再次感謝各刀登會員通力合作，會然氣象人生默默整理，我係刀登仔呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上回講到！<br />\n<br />\nViuTV奇幻愛情穿越劇《二月廿九》x《940920》討論(97)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2254974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2254974</a><br />\n<br />\n寶庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nViuTV奇幻愛情穿越劇《二月廿九》寶庫區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1983324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1983324</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免費重溫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/encore/leap-day\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fleap-day&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=04dc1b33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/encore/leap-day</a><br />\n<br />\n預告發放<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2523424837765810/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FViuTV.hk%2Fvideos%2F2523424837765810%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=85bc22c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2523424837765810/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張麗紗Yeesa（吳海昕 飾），2月29日出生的平凡少女。2017年，Yeesa於2月28日為自己慶祝生日，在11時59分一刻，竟然穿越時空，來到天寒地凍的北海道，過程中遇上和她未來命脈相連的兩個男人－馬智浩Ryan（徐天佑 飾）與余家聰（劉俊謙 飾），兩個香港男生都不約而同地聲稱與她相識。24小時過去，Yeesa穿越回到香港，現實卻只過了一秒鐘。Yeesa發現自己的穿越能力不由自主，而她竟然在現實裡重新認識Ryan及家聰&hellip;&hellip;命運的齒輪在靜靜地轉動著&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n導演及各演員們IG or YouTube<br />\n<br />\n導演 羅嘉駿 @stev.law<br />\n編劇 黃智揚 @yellow_wong_yellow<br />\n副導演兼 Alien - 鄭文熙 @manscheng<br />\n製作人兼 關羽 - 關永宇 @yukwanwing<br />\n演員:<br />\nYeesa - 吳海昕 Sofiee Ng @sofiee_ng <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Sofieeyan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FSofieeyan&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=f0cd8791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/Sofieeyan</a><br />\nRyan - 徐天佑 Chui Tien You @chuihammer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCi-u7xxaBviW9Ov1yL-5Bow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCi-u7xxaBviW9Ov1yL-5Bow&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=bdfda0fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCi-u7xxaBviW9Ov1yL-5Bow</a><br />\n余家聰/會長 - 劉俊謙 Terrance Lau @lauchunhim.terrance<br />\n巴西龜 - 岑珈其 @kakisham<br />\nFiona - 李敏 @ranyayaya<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/yatotheworld\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fyatotheworld&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=9e48d8d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/yatotheworld</a><br />\n嘉嘉 - 張凱娸 @kikicheungg<br />\nJonathan - 柯煒林 @willallwailam<br />\n馬芷晴 - 麥可怡 @krincee<br />\n老豆/辰叔 - 張松枝 @deon_cheung<br />\n耶穌 - 梁天尺 @tinchakleung<br />\n跳掣 - 蘇欣婷 @esthersogun<br />\nThomas - Dee(ERROR) @deegor_hkwa<br />\nTimothy - 梁嘉進 @ericlkc<br />\nRyan媽 - 吳浣儀<br />\n南野美子 (Yeesa 媽) - 沖崎千夏<br />\n香川二郎 (日本司機) - 山野久治"},{"pid":"336dd37b0ec13fb083892f5625446d380b35d9cc","tid":2264434,"uid":58584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">吳海昕世界第一</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrPYM2V.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrPYM2V.gif&h=fe4f5bdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"629fe37f7e4eeacdf285fc5550a7f1096ce2a8cf","tid":2264434,"uid":101981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat